data.description: LOCATION AND STYLE! This end unit, three story townhome is in close proximity to St. John’s Town Center and Top Golf. Upon entering you will immediately notice the craftsmanship with engineered hard wood flooring in the hallway with wall panel molding and closet. The flooring continues into the first-floor guest suite (4th Bedroom) with a full bath, closet and sliders to your private covered screened lanai that overlooks preserve. Also perfect for an in-law’s suite, etc. Stairway to second level is also engineered hardwood. The second level is the prime living and entertainment area. The kitchen features tile flooring, stainless steel appliances, wood cabinetry and granite countertop and breakfast bar. Breakfast bar opens to living room/dining room. These rooms also have engineered wood flooring, crown molding and sliders to a 12x6 open balcony. Off the kitchen you also have a bright 1/2 bath with a large window.  The third level has 3 additional bedrooms, 2 baths and a laundry closet area. The Owners’ Suite has high ceilings, double granite vanity sink, tile shower with tub and phenomenal, custom closet. Bedrooms 2 and 3 are generously sized. One is currently used as an office. A large  linen closet and an additional full bath complete this well thought out floor plan.  Your amenities include a community pool and fitness center. The HOA has recently installed a new roof and has begun painting and repairing stucco throughout the complex.  This location lends itself to a longer driveway allowing parking for two cars. All room measurements are taken to outside of closet- no interior feet. Living area reported does not include the total 152 feet for screen porch and balcony. Please be advised audio and visual monitoring (Ring) on premises. Home Warranty transferrable to Buyer Expires 1/2025
